    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="w-40 h-40 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-sage shadow-xl">
        <img
          src="/pictures/bobby-ai.JPG"
          alt="Bobby Galli"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-timber mb-4">
        About Me
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-stone">
        Software developer, AI enthusiast, and outdoor adventurer
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Story -->
    <section class="prose max-w-none mb-16">
      <h2>My Story</h2>
      <p>
        Hey there! I'm Bobby Galli, a software developer based in Providence, RI, though my roots run deep in the woods of New Hampshire. I'm a friendly, hard-working, curious, and entrepreneurial minded individual trying to leave the world a little better than I found it.
      </p>
      <p>
        By day, I'm a Principal Software Engineer at <a href="https://bugsplat.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BugSplat</a>, where I build crash and error reporting tools that help development teams ship better software. I've been with the team since 2017, and it's been an incredible journey building tools that developers actually love to use.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the side, I run <a href="https://workingdevshero.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Working Dev's Hero</a>, my consulting company where I help businesses tackle tough technical challenges. Whether it's building a new feature, debugging a gnarly issue, or architecting a system from scratch — I love solving problems.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm also a huge AI enthusiast. I love testing out the latest tools and exploring how they can make developers more productive. You'll often find me writing about software development, AI, and the ever-evolving tech landscape.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Education & Experience -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-timber mb-8">Education & Experience</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- BugSplat -->
        <div class="card p-6">
